OL,3,CMother sentenced to 10 years after
OL,4,Cdeaths of her four sons in housefire
OL,6,FA woman whose four young boys died in
OL,7,Fa fire after she left them home alone
OL,8,Fto go to Sainsbury's has been
OL,9,Fsentenced to 10 years in prison.
OL,11,FDeveca Rose had left her two sets of
OL,12,Ftwins in the locked terraced house
OL,13,Fwhen the fatal blaze broke out on the
OL,14,Fevening of December 16 2021.
OL,16,FThe 30-year-old defendant, who had
OL,17,Fsplit up with her partner and suffered
OL,18,Ffrom mental health problems, was found
OL,19,Fguilty of four counts of manslaughter
OL,20,Ffollowing an Old Bailey trial.
