OL,6,FRose turned away and concealed her
OL,7,Fface in a mask and padded hood as she
OL,8,Fsat in the dock of Court One at the
OL,9,FOld Bailey.
OL,11,FRose and the children had been living
OL,12,Fin squalor, surrounded by rubbish and
OL,13,Fhuman excrement, before the tragedy.
OL,15,FProsecutor Kate Lumsdon KC had told
OL,16,Fthe court: "There was rubbish thickly
OL,17,Fspread throughout the house. The
OL,18,Ftoilet and the bath were full of
OL,19,Frubbish and could not be used. Buckets
OL,20,Fand pots were used as toilets instead."
