OL,6,FRose had gone to the supermarket,
OL,7,Fleaving Leyton and Logan Hoath, aged
OL,8,Fthree; and four-year-olds Kyson and
OL,9,FBryson Hoath at the rented home in
OL,10,FSutton, south-west London.
OL,12,FWhen a cigarette or tea light in the
OL,13,Fliving room sparked a fire, the boys
OL,14,Fwere trapped and ran upstairs calling
OL,15,Ffor help.
OL,17,FA neighbour tried to break down the
OL,18,Ffront door before firefighters in
OL,19,Fbreathing apparatus went in and found
OL,20,Fthe children's bodies under beds.
