OL,6,FThey were rushed to two separate
OL,7,Fhospitals but attempts to save them
OL,8,Ffailed and they died from inhalation
OL,9,Fof fumes later that night.
OL,11,FRose arrived home while firefighters
OL,12,Fwere still tackling the blaze and she
OL,13,Fwas taken in by a neighbour.
OL,15,FShe had claimed she left the children
OL,16,Fwith a friend called Jade, which
OL,17,Fprompted firefighters to go back into
OL,18,Fthe house to search for her.
