OL,6,FPolice carried out extensive inquiries
OL,7,Fto find Jade and concluded she either
OL,8,Fdid not exist or had not been at the
OL,9,Fhouse that day.
OL,11,FIn police interviews, Rose admitted
OL,12,Fleaving the boys alone in the house on
OL,13,Ftwo earlier occasions.
OL,15,FThe children's father, Dalton Hoath,
OL,16,Fsaid in a statement that she had left
OL,17,Fthem alone once or twice to go to the
OL,18,Fnearby shop before.
