OL,6,FMr Hoath, who had split up with the
OL,7,Fdefendant, added that he was
OL,8,F"devastated" and his world had been
OL,9,Fturned "upside down" by the loss of
OL,10,Fhis "young, boisterous lads".
OL,12,FJurors were told that social worker
OL,13,FGeorgia Singh had raised concerns
OL,14,Fabout the family but the case was
OL,15,Fclosed three months before the fire.
OL,17,FPreviously, a health visitor had
OL,18,Fraised concerns about the family but
OL,19,Fthey were not followed up after she
OL,20,Fretired, jurors were told.
